#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&klettres; has 4 levels. Levels 1 and 2 deal with the alphabet and levels 3 and "
"4 concern syllables. For a very young child (2 1/2 to 4), I would suggest that "
"he/she is sitting on your lap in front of the computer and that you do the game "
"together."
msgstr ""

